黑社會勾結懲罰香港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你唔入黎元朗警署投訴<br />\n以後港共政權就係用呢班黑社會打， 甚至殺你地<br />\n之後警黑合作又唔拉人<br />\n香港就玩完"},{"pid":"379400d726585b42d44f9cb8bc548daa8adea8e5","tid":1361512,"uid":278765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T21:05:13.000Z","msg":"原先約好比較老弱嘅，一個ton 呔，一個我叫佢諗清楚，之後佢ton 呔。諗起「十個救火的少年」我諗到好多藉口，「我唔去，唔代表救唔到火」「我唔去，唔代表我屈服於恐懼」「我都唔係少年」&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我知共橙呢次目的手段，最壞可能性&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我怕死，但更怕活在恐懼之中。"},{"pid":"62b567c9561e6dc037bde37c0789db6c99f5666b","tid":1361512,"uid":8532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T21:08:59.000Z","msg":"驚係驚，出左反對有少少怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但良心同我講，唔可以唔去"},{"pid":"ad0213fb7c2a5d814b3e9c728c99ff6791c1331f","tid":1361512,"uid":258098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T21:19:00.000Z","msg":"香港人唔好再on9 <br />\n出街要伸請 <br />\n去睇戲要伸請 <br />\n去食飯要伸請<br />\n去坐車要伸請<br />\n去迪士尼要伸請<br />\n去海洋公園要伸請<br />\n去元朗要伸請<br />\n做咩要伸請 想去邊就去邊<br />\n我就係有幾百萬嘅網友 <br />\n相約網聚 吹咩<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">《緊急》堅持人強馬壯 新加聯署齊推<br />\n麻煩大家推726 728個post上熱門同時將消息散開各處</span></strong><br />\n￼<br />\n🥳7.26 10:00 新鴻基地產V Walk！商場開幕<br />\n🥳7.26 13:00 香港國際機場集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354831\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354831</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n🥳7.28 母忘上環 - 追究上環開槍責任<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356713</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n🎆香港🎆時代革命🎆爭取五大訴求🎆<br />\n📢1. 全面撤回送中條例<br />\n📢2. 撤銷6.12暴動定性&nbsp;<br />\n📢3. 釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究&nbsp;<br />\n📢4. 全面實行雙普選&nbsp;<br />\n📢5. 成立獨立調查委員會，追究黑警濫用暴力，徹查警黑勾結7.21元朗恐襲<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">睇到最底 內容包括：「運動時間」 「聯署」 《會加入新聯署 記得去簽》 白宮需要係電郵內確認先叫完成 就得係電郵㩒連結 唔好懶 所有活動必須同時進行</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻☻<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">持續不合作運動「兄弟爬山，各自努力」<br />\n🥳 - 18區連儂場<br />\n🥳 - 沙田新城市廣場</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n🥳7.26 新鴻基地產V Walk！商場開幕<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K1Gd4JR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK1Gd4JR.jpg&h=1881a8cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n🥳7.26 香港國際機場集會&nbsp;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354831\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354831</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eXxMFgZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeXxMFgZ.png&h=230e6ef8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n🥳7.27 元朗反恐襲 - 踢走鄉黑大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1355504\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1355504</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQjrFro.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQjrFro.jpg&h=1bb7313f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n🥳7.28 母忘上環 - 追究上環開槍責任<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356713</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YkqB2v6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYkqB2v6.jpg&h=a80f3aed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n🥳8.4 將軍澳反送中大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356143&nbsp;\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356143&nbsp;</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n🥳8.4 港島西大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356505\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356505</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xxAePbd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxxAePbd.png&h=0487fe92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請各位努力推po以提出遊行時間修訂<br />\n已取消或延期:<br />\n<br />\n兩條戰線同樣重要 但係請各位心水清&nbsp;<br />\n任何一方都不能忽視 以防誤中港共圈套<br />\n亦避免被各方妖孽分散注意力 必須將火力對準政權<br />\n政府務必回應五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n簽咗都要🙏廣傳🙏快夠數💪唔好話冇用就唔做，唔理效果有咩都必撐，團結是力量💪<br />\n<br />\n🖕🖕🖕見指中聯辦😡😡勾結香港黑社會😡😡策劃元朗恐怖襲擊聯署🖕🖕🖕<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 23, 2019：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/restore-hong-kongs-autonomy-make-hong-kong-great-again-0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frestore-hong-kongs-autonomy-make-hong-kong-great-again-0&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0MFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=49e5d2d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/restore-hong-kongs-autonomy-make-hong-kong-great-again-0</a><br />\n<br />\n🧐🧐【元朗黑夜連登獨立調查委員會】🧐🧐<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 23, 2019：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/34AmN69rRScNafEC9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F34AmN69rRScNafEC9&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0MFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=8cef2735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/34AmN69rRScNafEC9</a><br />\n<br />\n🤬🤬要求馬會撤銷何君堯會藉🤬🤬<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 23, 2019：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSchg3S-rvjk7DOky6yBCoby8EQMytbBE1eyYGyQe5rkIpSFcg/viewform?fbclid=IwAR0miS_G0dUlNRbwJeACAkr3xwKFgJRHHW4pIB7RjQoJNfoJSBFyWzDDzY4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSchg3S-rvjk7DOky6yBCoby8EQMytbBE1eyYGyQe5rkIpSFcg%2Fviewform%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0miS_G0dUlNRbwJeACAkr3xwKFgJRHHW4pIB7RjQoJNfoJSBFyWzDDzY4&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0MFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=e1d260bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSchg3S-rvjk7DOky6yBCoby8EQMytbBE1eyYGyQe5rkIpSFcg/viewform?fbclid=IwAR0miS_G0dUlNRbwJeACAkr3xwKFgJRHHW4pIB7RjQoJNfoJSBFyWzDDzY4</a><br />\n<br />\n😡😡投訴李漢民有違法公職人員行為失當😡😡<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 23, 2019：<br />\nEmail : csbcomp@csb.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n🙏🙏所有香港大學學生、舊生以及職員參與聯署，要求香港大學校長張翔履行社會使命。🙏🙏<a href=\"https://forms.gle/UAVikwsyCmdDEyy76\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FUAVikwsyCmdDEyy76&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0MFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=68703b5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/UAVikwsyCmdDEyy76</a><br />\n<br />\n🤭我唔捨得何君堯去美國🤭<br />\n🥳大家快聯署留底佢全家🥳<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 21, 2019：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/make-junius-ho-kwan-yiu-and-his-immediate-family-members-ineligible-us-entry-citizenship-and-visas?fbclid=IwAR0fZRhrobDg_hxUKcYKAN0XV833ZjHwxWu4XY82PzypubZpwq4ToZ8-e7M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fmake-junius-ho-kwan-yiu-and-his-immediate-family-members-ineligible-us-entry-citizenship-and-visas%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0fZRhrobDg_hxUKcYKAN0XV833ZjHwxWu4XY82PzypubZpwq4ToZ8-e7M&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0MFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=ac57db7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/make-junius-ho-kwan-yiu-and-his-immediate-family-members-ineligible-us-entry-citizenship-and-visas?fbclid=IwAR0fZRhrobDg_hxUKcYKAN0XV833ZjHwxWu4XY82PzypubZpwq4ToZ8-e7M</a><br />\n<br />\n🥰🤩[遍地攬炒] 一人一信幫何君堯律師世世代代享受大灣區榮耀🥰🤩😁內含教學😁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351572</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n🎊 On&nbsp;July 21, 2019：人道支援聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/requesting-international-humanitarian-aidassistance-unprotected-hong-kong-citizens\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequesting-international-humanitarian-aidassistance-unprotected-hong-kong-citizens&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0MFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=23f4aa40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/requesting-international-humanitarian-aidassistance-unprotected-hong-kong-citizens</a>"},{"pid":"33bffbb269118237d3c2c4c92eac1e910bef2962","tid":1361512,"uid":174447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T21:34:02.000Z","msg":"我驚死我好驚比人打比人捅又驚比人拉<br />\n咁又點 team up 加 full gear 加 be water囉<br />\n咁容易咁輕鬆又點會係抗爭？<br />\n一定要去 齊上齊落 <br />\n一定要更加小心保護自己同身邊嘅朋友<br />\n<br />\n另外叫其他人諗清楚後果既人<br />\n咁你又覺得有咩後果可以嚴重得過個社會變到黑白顛倒是非不分？<br />\n暴政好恐怖 警黑勾結係好恐怖<br />\n但都恐怖唔過你明明知道件事好錯<br />\n但都去到關鍵時刻選擇逃避 唔企出黎反抗<br />\n到底幾時先明白<br />\n逃避就係等於妥協同埋繼續縱容呢個政權去剝削我地<br />\n唔好再為自己既懦弱揾藉口啦 個關鍵時刻嚟左喇"}]}